These are Puzzles for 1x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-1::.
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, snooker, bridge, canasta
1. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2  |   3   |   4   |  5  |
| Game   | snooker | mah-jongg | bridge | scrabble | canasta |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-2::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, alhambra, vegafina, davidoff, baccarat
1. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
2. the davidoff-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2  |     3     |     4     |     5      |
| Cigar   | davidoff | baccarat | alhambra | cain | vegafina |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, october, may, february, september
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
3. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |  3   |     4      |   5   |
| Birthday   | october | may | april | february | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-4::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, quad-bike, bus, helicopter
1. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |       1       |     2     |       3        |   4    |     5     |
| Transport   | bus | jet-ski | quad-bike | helicopter | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-5::.
House: wooden, townhouse, victorian, modern, futuristic
1. the futuristic house is in an even position##4
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the victorian house##1
3. the wooden house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
4. the townhouse house is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |  2   |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| House   | modern | futuristic | victorian | townhouse | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-6::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily, iris, rose, daffodil
1. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
4. the person who growsiris is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who growsrose##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3    |    4     |  5   |
| Flower   | bellflower | iris | rose | lily | daffodil |

