2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in may##2
4. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4     |   5    |
| Birthday   | july | august | march | may | december |

