.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: classical, trance, house, folk, r&b
1. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
2. the fan of house is in an even position##4
3. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
4. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of trance##1
5. the fan of r&b is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |   2    |     3     |   4   |     5     |
| Music-Genre   | folk | trance | r&b | house | classical |

