.:: Puzzle 1x5-Level-4-20::.
City: berlin, london, boston, nizza, venice
1. the person traveling to venice is between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to boston##2
2. the person traveling to nizza is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to nizza##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2  |    3     |    4     |   5    |
| City   | london | venice | boston | nizza | berlin |

 